{"tid":1124417,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[開台喇開台喇] Leisure Radio 休閒電台","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:33:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-04T15:56:22.000Z","uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"181bea4fb5451a714316925d9b366e56ab546d99","tid":1124417,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"打左重點喺度先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n預計今晚開台時間係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">22:00-00:00</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Discord傳送門</span></strong>︰ <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqzeyzgN&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5STHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=47b558ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN</a></span><br />\n<br />\n-----------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n是咁的<br />\n小弟近日喺度整理下自己嘅物品<br />\n執執下竟然搵到自己以前自己用過嘅JTV Account <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n以前開台嘅回憶即刻湧曬出嚟<br />\n突然間好想好似以前咁喺JTV開台<br />\n同大家一齊嘻嘻哈哈過下日晨<br />\n但可惜JTV而家已經連影都無 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就喺我想打消返呢個念頭之際<br />\n發現左Discord其實都做到一樣嘅功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n甚至運作上更加流暢<br />\n延遲亦都更加低<br />\n所以我就嗱嗱聲開左個Channel<br />\n命名為 '<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Leisure Radio 休閒電台</span></span></strong>'<br />\n顧名思義呢度係一個比大家放低平日重擔嘅平台<br />\n希望大家有興趣都可以賞個面入嚟吹下水一齊放鬆下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有鑑於小弟嘅工作關係<br />\n做唔到每日都喺固定時間開台<br />\n所以只要決定左幾時會開台就會透過以下渠道Update大家︰<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Discord</span></strong>: <a href=\"https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdiscord.gg%2FqzeyzgN&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5STHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=47b558ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://discord.gg/qzeyzgN</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">Telegram</span></strong>: <a href=\"https://t.me/LeisureRadio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FLeisureRadio&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5STHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=7e82f57f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/LeisureRadio</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家初步估計呢個Channel主要都係用電台嘅方式同大家傾下偈<br />\n未必每一次都有特定嘅主題<br />\n起初呢度可能會更偏向一個吹水平台咁<br />\n而開台期間唔少得嘅當然係Phone-in環節啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n會比大家上嚟Share下自己大大小小嘅趣事<br />\n又或者有煩惱都可以喺度同大家傾訴下<br />\n想上嚟發洩下唱下歌都得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外我地都會用下Discord嘅Function嚟播下歌又或者播下片咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果大家有咩建議又或者有咩疑問，亦都可以透過上面兩個途徑去直接聯絡我 (Telegram嘅話可以撳呢條Link搵到我：<a href=\"https://t.me/hasumisan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhasumisan&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5STHxASuYsPIDBrSRMhTQaAk%3D&h=6fb9fedf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hasumisan</a>)"},{"pid":"b36f2c700839ce3caf6c2d34a8eb0693c1f69d17","tid":1124417,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T05:29:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b675b25a3959cd1875b4a6a1bf923e6e96f7d36","tid":1124417,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4e11038326477767ca319942653afbb8861034a","tid":1124417,"uid":250047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T07:32:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"